.PP
.if n *
.if t \(bu
.\" Change 30
The \fIc_incl\fP program now has a \fB-quote-filenames\fP option, which
means that you can have filenames with spaces and special characters
in them.
.PP
.if n *
.if t \(bu
.\" Change 28
A bug in the \fIc_incl\fP program's path flattening has been fixed.
.PP
.if n *
.if t \(bu
.\" change 26
A small Y2K bug has been fixed in the date parsing used by the
\fIcooktime\fP(1) command.
.PP
.if n *
.if t \(bu
.\" change 25
A bug which caused the -parallel option to lose track of processes when
you used [execute] in a recipe body has been fixed.
.PP
.if n *
.if t \(bu
.\" change 17
The restrictions on the placement of the placement of %0 in a pattern
have been dropped; too many people didn't like it.  This does \fInot\fP
break any cookbooks.
.PP
.if n *
.if t \(bu
.\" change 15
Cook now copes with the absence of the HOME environment variable.
This was a problem for CGI scripts.
